text: Emiliano García-Page Sánchez (born 11 June 1968) is a Spanish politician from the Spanish Socialist Workers' Party who is the President of Castile-La Mancha since 2015. García-Page was the Mayor of Toledo from 2007 to 2015; after the 2015 city council election he was succeeded in the position by Milagros Tolón. ==References== ==External links== * Emiliano García-Page Sánchez Junta of Communities of Castile-La Mancha website Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish Socialist Workers' Party politicians Category:Presidents of Castilla–La Mancha Category:Government ministers of Castilla–La Mancha Category:Members of the 5th Cortes of Castilla–La Mancha Category:Members of the 6th Cortes of Castilla–La Mancha Category:Members of the 9th Cortes of Castilla–La Mancha Category:Members of the Cortes of Castilla–La Mancha from Toledo Category:Toledo city councillors Category:Public works ministers of Spanish autonomous communities Category:Mayors of places in Castilla–La Mancha Category:Members of the 10th Cortes of Castilla–La Mancha
